01:48:17.616 --> 01:48:19.200
Well, she seems to
think otherwise.

01:48:19.284 --> 01:48:21.244
Well, she's not.

01:48:21.328 --> 01:48:22.954
What do you want me to tell her?

01:48:23.038 --> 01:48:25.707
Tell her she's not
fucking speaking.

01:48:25.791 --> 01:48:27.500
Okay, well, you both
seem pretty certain...

01:48:27.584 --> 01:48:30.128
Well, let my certainty
supersede her certainty.

01:48:30.212 --> 01:48:31.546
Goddamn it.

01:48:36.176 --> 01:48:37.593
Steve.

01:48:37.678 --> 01:48:39.679
You want to see me?

01:48:39.763 --> 01:48:41.305
Yes. This way.

