and the other extremists.

01:51:37.566 --> 01:51:40.067
They'll destroy the
party if you let them.

01:51:41.278 --> 01:51:43.863
Remember, you're a hockey mum.

01:51:43.947 --> 01:51:45.948
You just wanted to
make a difference,

01:51:46.033 --> 01:51:47.867
and you did.

01:51:47.951 --> 01:51:49.452
A big, huge difference.

01:51:49.536 --> 01:51:51.871
I'll always be
grateful. Thank you.

